text:
You may opt to utilize the "Forgot Password?" option to retrieve the new temporary password and unlock the account at the same time.

Here are the instructions:
1. Tap the 'Forgot Password?' option.
2. The system will request the username and e-mail address you are using. Please note that it should match the one registered in our database to be able to continue. 
3. Tap "Send to Email Address" once finalized.
4. Should there be no error, you may now check the temporary password sent to your email account.
